name: Jump Over .IO
description:
If you like simple io games with addictive gameplay, the Jump over.io is for you! The aim of the game is to survive on the arena by jumping over the sharp blades and knives, which move around the circle platform and slice the characters. Try not to fall and jump over the all obstacles.

There is only one way to become a champion: you need to stay as long as possible on the arena which is falling apart under your feet and not fall. You’re not the one on the arena: your enemies will be trying to defeat you! Beat them all! Stay as long as you can on the platform and don’t fall!

Jump over.io is easy to play: just overcome the moving sharp blades and don’t fall down. The last on the platform will be the winner! Ready for the challenge?

Game features:
 - Simple and fun game!
- Addictive gameplay!
-Colorful locations!
- Easy controls!
- Amazing graphics!
-User friendly interface!

Jump over.io will move your passtime to the next level! So what are you waiting for? Tap the install button and enjoy the game!
